text: Immanuel Lutheran College may refer to: * Immanuel Lutheran College (Hong Kong), a secondary school in Hong Kong * Immanuel Lutheran College (Eau Claire), a high school, college and seminary in Eau Claire, Wisconsin *Immanuel Lutheran College, Buderim, a primary and secondary college run by the Lutheran Church of Australia ==See also== * Immanuel College (disambiguation)
title: Immanuel Lutheran College
